_sText:
This is my first map ever. Not just my first release, but the first map I ever attempted to make.

Feedback is awesome, so if you have anything to tip me about let me know.

Blaze gave me the idea to make it called Red_vs_Blue, so I wanted to tweak the map around it. If you like what you see then comment. If you want me to make more themed maps, just leave me comments.

Coming up in V2: +Background Music +Fixed Lighting +Custom Walls/Floors/Ceilings +Add Objects that make it seem more RvB like -Remove some of the random objects
